OpenSuSE</link> and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../298/990298.xml">
Ubuntu</link><ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%229%22])">9</ref> can be run on the PlayStation 3.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%2210%22])">10</ref> <O wordnetid="106832680" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../708/246708.xml">
Yellow Dog Linux</link></O>
 for the PlayStation 3 was first released for the PS3 in late 2006.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%2211%22])">11</ref>
</p>
<ss1>
<st>
 Ubuntu </st>
<p>

<image location="right" width="200px" src="Ubuntu_Logo.svg">
