<sec>
<st>
 RSX Homebrew </st>
<p>

Linux on the PlayStation 3 allows for a huge range of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../667/1495667.xml">
homebrew</link> programs to be developed and is entirely and completely sanctioned by Sony. Although the <chip wordnetid="103020034" confidence="0.8">
